<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 15:11:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Zara 母公司 Inditex 大幅削减中国门店 聚焦数字化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-slashes-china-stores-digital-focus-2024-03-14/</link><description>Zara 母公司 Inditex 去年在中国的税前利润增长了一倍多，尽管这家时尚零售商缩减了实体店规模，关闭了其在中国五分之一的门店，这表明其对在线销售的关注正在取得成果。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 14:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-slashes-china-stores-digital-focus-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟调查速卖通可能存在的非法在线产品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-probes-aliexpress-over-possibly-illegal-online-products-2024-03-14/</link><description>周四，欧盟委员会对传播潜在非法和色情材料展开调查，这是继社交媒体平台 X 和 TikTok 之后的第三次此类调查，阿里巴巴旗下速卖通可能面临巨额罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 13:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-probes-aliexpress-over-possibly-illegal-online-products-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>据 CNBC 报道，前财政部长姆努钦正在召集投资者购买 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-treasury-secretary-mnuchin-putting-together-investors-buy-tiktok-cnbc-2024-03-14/</link><description>美国前财政部长史蒂文·姆努钦 (Steven Mnuchin) 周四对 CNBC 表示，他正在组建一个投资者团体，试图收购 TikTok。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-treasury-secretary-mnuchin-putting-together-investors-buy-tiktok-cnbc-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲监管机构称批准中国客机需要时间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/europe-regulator-says-will-take-time-needed-approve-china-jet-2024-03-14/</link><description>欧洲航空安全监管机构高级官员告诉路透社，欧洲航空安全监管机构将不惜一切时间批准中国C919客机，这挫伤了北京方面迅速打入因飞机短缺和波音安全危机而出现的市场的希望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/europe-regulator-says-will-take-time-needed-approve-china-jet-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国首次承办戴维斯杯决赛小组赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/china-host-davis-cup-finals-group-stage-matches-first-time-2024-03-14/</link><description>国际网球联合会（ITF）周四表示，中国将于9月首次举办戴维斯杯决赛小组赛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/china-host-davis-cup-finals-group-stage-matches-first-time-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于出口影响力引发摩擦，中国汽车制造商在海外开设工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-open-factories-abroad-export-clout-causes-friction-2024-03-14/</link><description>随着外国监管机构考虑对进口中国制造的电动汽车采取措施，寻求全球增长的中国汽车制造商正在海外市场建设更多汽车工厂。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-open-factories-abroad-export-clout-causes-friction-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>分析师称，中国削减汽车首付的计划可能会落空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</link><description>分析师表示，中国通过削减汽车贷款首付来促进汽车销售的努力可能会因价格战和消费者谨慎而受挫，这主要有利于特斯拉和蔚来等少数受年轻买家青睐的品牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普发起中央情报局针对中国的秘密影响行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-launched-cia-covert-influence-operation-against-china-2024-03-14/</link><description>据直接了解这项高度机密行动的前美国官员透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统上任两年后，授权中央情报局在中国社交媒体上发起秘密活动，旨在扭转中国公众舆论反对中国政府。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-launched-cia-covert-influence-operation-against-china-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：石油玷污了通胀观点，特斯拉处于慢车道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-14/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国餐馆爆炸后媒体骚扰引发抗议和公众批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/media-harassment-after-china-restaurant-blast-sparks-protest-public-criticism-2024-03-14/</link><description>记者在试图报道北京郊外爆炸事件的后果时被当地居民和保安拦住，负责监管中国记者的协会发表了罕见的抗议声明。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/media-harassment-after-china-restaurant-blast-sparks-protest-public-criticism-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>意大利监管机构因内容检查对 TikTok 罚款 1100 万美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/italy-regulator-fines-tiktok-11-mln-over-inadequate-checks-harmful-content-2024-03-14/</link><description>意大利竞争监管机构周四表示，因对可能对年轻或弱势用户有害的内容检查不充分，对社交媒体巨头 TikTok 的三个部门处以总计 1000 万欧元（1094 万美元）的罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/italy-regulator-fines-tiktok-11-mln-over-inadequate-checks-harmful-content-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>越南敦促中国在划定北部湾基线时尊重国际法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-respect-international-law-china-draws-gulf-tonkin-baseline-2024-03-14/</link><description>越南外交部周四在回应有关中国本月早些时候划定北部湾基线的问题时表示，国际法和其他国家的权益必须得到尊重。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-respect-international-law-china-draws-gulf-tonkin-baseline-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国周三发射DRO-A/B卫星未成功——官方媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-dro-ab-satellite-wednesday-not-successful-state-media-2024-03-14/</link><description>据官方新华社周四报道，中国周三在西昌卫星发射中心发射的 DRO-A/B 卫星没有成功。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:33:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-dro-ab-satellite-wednesday-not-successful-state-media-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称美国提议的 TikTok 禁令“不公平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/proposed-us-tiktok-ban-not-fair-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-14/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周四表示，以国家安全为由削弱其他国家的竞争优势，“毫无公平可言”，并批评美国强制剥离或禁止 TikTok 的法案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/proposed-us-tiktok-ban-not-fair-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国腾讯收购字节跳动两个视频游戏团队 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-tencent-takes-over-two-bytedance-video-game-teams-source-2024-03-14/</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，在字节跳动去年退出游戏业务后，中国腾讯已经接管了字节跳动的两家视频游戏部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-tencent-takes-over-two-bytedance-video-game-teams-source-2024-03-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>